content: Sporting event delegation **[Singapore](/wiki/Singapore)** competed at the **[1966 British Empire and Commonwealth Games](/wiki/1966_British_Empire_and_Commonwealth_Games)** in [Kingston, Jamaica](/wiki/Kingston,_Jamaica), for the first time as an independent state. It participated in six sports but did not win any medals. This [Commonwealth Games](/wiki/Commonwealth_Games)-related article is a stub.
